snippet.title: Tadpole Treble 2014 Teaser
snippet.description:
It's Tadpole Treble, the first video game from the brothers at BitFinity! This musical action game tasks players to avoid the notes of the game's original music to help a young tadpole through her quest. By the creator of the popular webcomic Brawl in the Family.

Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=196181437
Tadpole Treble Website: http://bitfinitygames.com
Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/TadpoleTreble?ref=tn_tnmn
